 Anambra – In what will come across as a really shocking development, a man has been caught trying to sleep with his friend’s wife. The man who was simply identitfied as Aboy, was given the humilation in his life after he was caught in the act. Local reports show that the inident happened in Anambra state. The man said to be an indigene of Nnewi community of Anambra State was caught in the act by his best friend whose wife he was trying to sleep with at a guest house in the state. After alarm was raised, a crowd gathered and he was shamed before being handed over to the police. Source